verbose_text: Given the regulatory effects of visfatin on Bcl-2/Bax/caspase-3, the present data showing that pre-treatment with the inhibitors, FK866 or BAY11-7085, effectively suppressed visfatin induced apoptosis, as well as ICAM-1 and IL-6 protein expression, support the notion that NF-kappaB in part mediates visfatin induced apoptosis.
